fields.name: task-launch
fields.title: Task Launch
fields.description: A task for this job execution failed to launch.

fields.name: docker-task-launch
fields.title: Docker Task Launch
fields.description: A Docker task for this job execution failed to launch a Docker container.

fields.name: node-lost
fields.title: Node Lost
fields.description: The node failed and was lost, causing this job execution to be lost.

fields.name: timeout
fields.title: Timeout
fields.description: The job execution exceeded its timeout threshold.

fields.name: algorithm-unknown
fields.title: Algorithm Failure
fields.description: The algorithm failed by returning a non-zero exit code. To allow Scale to detect more specific problems with the algorithm, please define the appropriate errors for the non-zero exit codes that the algorithm may return.

fields.name: invalid-results-manifest
fields.title: Algorithm Failure
fields.description: The output files from the result manifest are invalid. This could mean either duplicate output names were found, no output files were found, or both 'file' and 'files' object were found in the output_data

fields.name: missing-required-output
fields.title: Algorithm Failure
fields.description: The output_data parameter is missing from the results manifest file
